    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Rinse your<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain, return it to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/katsu-curry-inspired-double-chicken-and-stir-fry-veg-brown-rice-bowl/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> into discs on the diagonal</p><p>Slice each individual <strong>cucumber disc</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Add your <strong>cucumber matchsticks</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, a splash of <strong>boiled water </strong>and<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then set aside to pickle \u2013 this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/katsu-curry-inspired-double-chicken-and-stir-fry-veg-brown-rice-bowl/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a chopping board, cover with <strong>cling film </strong>and bash with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until flattened to approx. 1cm thickness</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/katsu-curry-inspired-double-chicken-and-stir-fry-veg-brown-rice-bowl/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>(Doubled your protein? Use 2 pans!)</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/katsu-curry-inspired-double-chicken-and-stir-fry-veg-brown-rice-bowl/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Combine your<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder </strong>and <strong>cornflour</strong> in a measuring jug</p><p>Gradually stir in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [255ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong>, 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and your <strong>soy sauce </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>katsu curry sauce base</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/katsu-curry-inspired-double-chicken-and-stir-fry-veg-brown-rice-bowl/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium-heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>shredded veg mix</strong> to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until the vegetables begin to soften</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>cooked rice</strong> to the pot and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the rice is piping hot \u2013 this is your <strong>stir fry veg rice</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/katsu-curry-inspired-double-chicken-and-stir-fry-veg-brown-rice-bowl/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Put the jug with the katsu curry sauce base in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 2 min, stirring halfway, or until the sauce has thickened \u2013<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>katsu curry sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/katsu-curry-inspired-double-chicken-and-stir-fry-veg-brown-rice-bowl/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>XL</strong> <strong>cooked chicken </strong>on top of the <strong>stir fry veg rice</strong> with the <strong>quick-pickled cucumber </strong>to the side</p><p>Pour the <strong>katsu curry sauce </strong>over the chicken and sprinkle with your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
